"This invoice lists material in ITEM_COUNT_WITH_TAG(Material) items. The net value is NETTO_SUM_PER_TAG(Material),\n"
"plus VAT_SUM_PER_TAG(Material) = BRUTTO_SUM_PER_TAG(Material).\n"
