#: kraft.adoc:703
msgid ""
"Kraft does not come with its own address book implementation, but uses an "
"established and mature solution called "
"https://apps.kde.org/de/kaddressbook/[KAddressbook] which is provided as "
"part of the PIM (Personal Information Management) software collection of "
"https://www.kde.org[KDE]. Integration with KAddressBook is the "
"recommendation and default of Kraft."
