#. type: Plain text
#: kraft.adoc:707
msgid ""
"However, in some situations the KAddressBook Integration can not be set up. "
"In that cases, Kraft can also read a address collection of a local "
"directory. The directory can be set in the Kraft config file in group "
"`[KraftV2]`, key `KraftV2AddressDir`. If not explicitely set, it defaults to "
"`$HOME/.local/share/contacts`."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: kraft.adoc:710
msgid ""
"This directory needs to contain single files in the vCard format, with file "
"extension `.vcf`. All these files are read and presented as addresses in "
"Kraft."
